+      MEMORY ALLOCATION
+         By default, we use malloc and free for memory allocation.  To override the
+         memory allocation, before the implementation #include, add a:
+
+            #define STBIR_MALLOC(size,user_data) ...
+            #define STBIR_FREE(ptr,user_data)   ...
